 Learn about the SourceGas acquisition
 


On Feb. 12, Black Hills Corp. completed the acquisition of SourceGas. 
With the addition of approximately 429,000 SourceGas customers, the combined entity will serve more than 1.2 million electric and gas utility customers in approximately 800 communities.


 




News


Flood Safety Warning for Eastern Iowa
As a safety precaution in the wake of flooding and potential flooding in Guttenberg, Fredericksburg, Sumner, Fayette and the surrounding area, Black Hills Energy employees have communicated with and temporarily shut off natural gas service to impacted customers.


