Investor Relations
We are a customer-focused, growth-oriented, vertically-integrated utility company with a tradition of exemplary service and a vision to be the energy partner of choice. Based in Rapid City, South Dakota, we serve approximately 1.2 million natural gas and electric utility customers in eight states. We also generate wholesale electricity and produce natural gas, crude oil and coal.



