Work With Us
We serve 1.2 million utility customers in nearly 800 communities throughout eight states. It’s important for us to establish solid relationships with local vendors, suppliers and economic development organizations. We also work diligently to provide a great place to work for our thousands of employees.
If you'd like to work with us or start a career in energy, we'd love to partner with you. 







Careers

If you want to make a difference in the communities we serve, we have a job for you. Help us improve life with energy.






Economic Development

When your business sets out to climb higher, choosing the right location is critical. And you need a utility that’s with you all the way.






