Contact Information

Customer Service
Quick and easy, the touchtone service puts the information you need at your fingertips. Just call Customer Service and follow the prompts.

Black Hills Energy: 888-890-5554 or Email Black Hills Energy

24-hour Emergency Assistance
If you smell gas, do not call from the premises. Leave immediately and call from a neighboring location. Never touch a downed powerline!

Black Hills Energy: 800-694-8989

Safety
Call 811 before you dig. It’s free, it’s easy, and it’s the law.

Service Guard: 800-504-2000
Appliance repair, repair protection plans, heating & cooling sales and service (regional availability). Visit the ServiceGuard website or Email Service Guard.

