Energy Career Resources


Careers


If you want to make a difference, then we have a career for you. For more than 130 years, we’ve dedicated ourselves to finding, producing, and distributing energy that powers our customers’ homes and businesses. Every member of our team is challenged to take our mission personally: to Improve Life with Energy. 
We live out this mission in our daily work, in community service and leadership, and in doing the right thing for our customers, co-workers, shareholders, and the environment.
"Work from Home" scam alert: Be aware that links to a "work from home" scam have been posted to certain Facebook accounts and job posting websites. These postings are not from Black Hills Energy or Black Hills Corporation. Click here to learn more.




