Home
Products & Services





Whether you’re looking for ways to protect your appliances from a breakdown or products that will improve your life with energy, we’ve got you covered.Dang. We don't offer products and services in your area.Whoops! Please enter a ZIP code to view products and services available in your area. 


Services
Let us help you protect your appliances from a breakdown, manage your energy usage and find great ways to fuel your home or business. Uh oh! You need to enter a ZIP code to view services available in your area.



Great uses for natural gas
If you’re already enjoying clean, reliable natural gas to heat your home and cook your meals, check out the other ways you can take advantage of the this super fuel.





Service Guard
Don’t worry about who to call when one of your home appliances breaks down. Call Service Guard. We offer affordable repair plans and repair services.





CAPP
Get a CAPP plan to keep your heating and cooling equipment from causing unexpected costs.





ASAP
Get peace of mind from unexpected costs heating and cooling equipment repair costs with an ASAP plan.





Technical Services
Contact us for practical, cost-effective solutions to your energy needs. 



Choice Gas
In Nebraska and Wyoming, you can choose the natural gas supplier that best meets your service and pricing needs.


Products
Choose from an array of energy products that can help you save money on your bill and add extra comfort to your home. Dang! We don't offer any products in your area.Uh oh! You need to enter a ZIP code to view products available in your area.



Cove Heating
Choose cove heating for a quick, easy, cost-effective heating alternative for virtually every room in your home. 



Heating and Cooling Products
Keep yourself warm in the winter and cool in summer by purchasing heating and cooling products from us.


Financing
If you're a qualified customer, you can choose from three financing options when you're ready to buy a new appliance.




LED Bulbs
You can save more than 60 percent on select LED bulbs when you buy them through our website.



Carbon Monoxide Detectors
Buy a carbon monoxide detector from us to protect yourself and your family from the deadly effects of carbon monoxide poisoning.




Demand Controller Program
Save 20 percent or more on your energy bill with a Demand Controller if your electric usage is 1,200 kilowatt-hours or more a month.





In-Floor Radiant Heat
When you want the comfort of an in-floor heating system without all the added expense, hassle and maintenance of a tube and boiler system, opt for in-floor radiant heat.





Heat Pumps
If your furnace is less than 10 years old, consider adding a heat pump to supplement your heating needs.





Geothermal
Consider a geothermal heating and cooling system. It uses a natural, renewable energy source — the Earth beneath you — all while saving you 30-60 percent on your energy bills.




For local information enter your zip code.




Did You Know?




Heating and cooling your home uses more energy and drains more energy dollars than any other system in your home. Typically, 44 percent of your energy bill goes for heating and cooling. Reducing use here saves you money on your utility bill.

