LAM Columns











Since 1985, Hills Products Group has strived to differentiate itself from competitors by providing one of a kind customer service as well as high quality lumber products.  Located in the beautiful Black Hills of South Dakota, Hills Products Group manufactures and distributes quality wood products, treated lumber, rough lumber, pattern stock, pine & spruce boards, and much more.












